description: Come check out our beautifully updated Mira Mesa Home!  Centrally located near schools and shopping, this HOME offers it all.  MOVE-IN ready! Step into this spacious and stylish 4-bedroom, 2-bath home perfectly situated in one of Mira Mesa’s most desirable neighborhoods. Freshly painted inside and out with a modern neutral palette, this home features brand-new vinyl plank flooring throughout, offering both durability and elegance.  The kitchen is a chef’s dream—fully equipped with sleek new stainless steel and black appliances, recessed lighting, and plenty of counter space. The airy living room boasts vaulted ceilings, generous natural light, and easy access to both the side and backyard through dual exits and sliding glass doors—perfect for indoor-outdoor living and entertaining. A dedicated dining area provides space for memorable gatherings.  Retreat to the oversized primary suite, complete with his-and-hers closets, a walk-in shower, and double sinks for added convenience. The three additional bedrooms are generously sized, and the front room offers flexibility as a fourth bedroom, office, or guest space. Enjoy energy efficiency with dual-pane windows and new mini blinds throughout. Outside, RV parking adds extra value and convenience, while the newly seeded front yard and fresh landscaping (soon to bloom) promise to make your curb appeal the envy of the neighborhood. All of this just minutes from shopping, restaurants, and parks—many within walking distance. This move-in ready gem combines comfort, style, and location.  But wait there's more.  This home has a brand new HVAC and water heater!  Don’t miss it!
